Gregtech wires work differently than other tech mods.  Gregtech 6 wires are available in exposed wires and insulated wires known as cables.  The wires are available in bundles from 1 to 16 wires.  The cables are available is 1x, 2x, 4x, 8x, and 16x cables.  Each cable has a maximum volatage (i.e. EU) that the wire/calbe to carry, amperage or the number of machines you can run off that wire/cable at the same time, and loss whic his the number of EU loss per meter of wire/cable.  So you want to check the maximum EU that you need and how many machines you are running to determine your cable that you use.
